For example, if the issue has

{noformat}
    "voters" : [ "fred", "idonotexist", "george" ]
{noformat}

And "idonotexist" does not exist, then "fred" will be included as a voter, but "george" is lost.  This should not happen at all, much less without a warning concerning "george", and it doesn't happen for the watchers.

