The importers can be configured to create users in JIRA. If a user named "Unassigned" or "unassigned" is created then the JIRA UI becomes hard to understand. 

I would like the JIRA Importers to check for and then not create such users.

The same is true of creating a JIRA Resolution named None or Unresolved as noted at https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Defining+Resolution+Field+Values

